00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:12,419
scientist-to-scientist.

456
00:17:13,466 --> 00:17:15,810
We're not talking
scientist-to-scientist.

457
00:17:15,901 --> 00:17:18,123
You're not a scientist.
You're just a rich man that

458
00:17:18,223 --> 00:17:20,544
no one will be honest to because
everyone wants your money.

459
00:17:24,032 --> 00:17:25,471
Oh, don't listen to him.

460
00:17:25,555 --> 00:17:26,908
I mean, he's just a kid.

461
00:17:26,992 --> 00:17:28,953
Why don't you tell me
a little more

462
00:17:29,038 --> 00:17:31,380
about your pyramid
thingy? Huh?

463
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:35,291
<i>"Footloose"
by Kenny Loggins playing...</i>

464
00:17:35,401 --> 00:17:38,432
<i>It turned out
